data.description: ****$2,000 Use As You Choose!!****This charming home offers the perfect mix of comfort and convenience. It features a cozy breakfast nook and formal dining room providing ample space for entertaining. The spacious master suite boasts vaulted ceilings, ensuring a relaxing and peaceful retreat. Located just a short commute away from local beaches and minutes from the beautiful historical downtown Swansboro, this home offers the perfect mix of convenience and comfort. The backyard comes with a privacy fence and best of all, no city taxes! To top it all off, this home was just painted! **Buyers can receive an additional $1,000 lender credit when using Jena Ashcraft with Movement Mortgage**
